Wine & Dishes, Private Kitchen]

2
00:00:17,696 --> 00:00:20,128
The famous novelist Zhang Ailing once said

3
00:00:20,848 --> 00:00:24,352
"Love is not complicated, it all
comes down to three words."

4
00:00:25,056 --> 00:00:27,808
"It's either 'I love you', 'I hate you',

5
00:00:28,352 --> 00:00:30,496
or 'let it be', 'how are you'.

6
00:00:31,808 --> 00:00:32,896
'I'm sorry'"

7
00:00:35,008 --> 00:00:37,792
Unfortunately, I can't write about love.

8
00:00:38,592 --> 00:00:42,388
All that's left in life are
various forms of 'I'm sorry'.

9
00:00:43,296 --> 00:00:46,464
[Episode 3 Another Form of Happiness]

10
00:00:46,464 --> 00:00:52,512
♫ Oh, time is a kind thief ♫

11
00:00:53,546 --> 00:00:59,424
♫ Stealing doubts and building up love ♫

12
